# Path C Slice 3 (decision 4): ATOMIC release = gripper open FUSED with a scene
# detach (AttachedCollisionObject REMOVE -> object falls back into the world).
# Gripper actuation is best-effort in fake sim; the detach is what matters.
#
# --- request ---
string  object_id                    # id of the attached collision object to release + detach
---
# --- response ---
bool    success                      # reflects the scene-detach op
bool    attached                     # false after a successful release
string  error_message                # surfaces partial state (e.g. gripper actuation skipped)
